Which of the following is a magic variable that populates the date and time of operating system?

A. ansible_time
B. ansible_date_time
C. ansible_chron
D. ansible_clock

Which is the keyword used for defining a condition in an ansible playbook?

A. for
B. while
C. when
D. if

We have an Ubuntu server; that requires qemu be installed. Will the following playbook install the requirement?

```
---
- name: Installing QEMU
  hosts: all
  tasks:
  - name: Installing QEMU
    package:
        name: qemu
        state: present
    when: ansible_os_family == "Debian"

```

A. Yes
B. No

